<plot>Stan and Ollie give evidence which convicts vicious gangster Butch (Walter Long). They plan to leave town and advertise for a travelling companion to share expenses. Butch's girl (Mae Busch) replies to the advert and the boys come to collect her. Butch meanwhile has escaped and when the boys finally succeed in freeing him from a trunk he exacts a terrible revenge.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?218426</url></doc>
